threats.title: Tampering
threats.description: E.g. modification of frontend navigation in order to cause redirection to phishing page
threats.mitigation: Open - need to confirm whether there is any tampering/data validation mechanism implemented

threats.title: Unauthorized access to sensitive data
threats.description: Compromise sensitive data due to faulty authorization process
threats.mitigation: Possible remedy - OAuth 2.0 + RBAC or ABAC (role-/attribute-based access control)

threats.title: DoS attempt
threats.description: Overload and disruption of high availability system
threats.mitigation: Each microservice is handled by separate load balancer
